1. Navigated to my repository:
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend

2. Created new directory:
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

3. Installed nvm (Node Version Manager):
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

4. Closed terminal and reopened it.

5. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0:
   nvm install 20.16.0

6. Installed SASS version 3.7.4:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
